6/12/china-has-become-a-scientific-superpower">一个关于中国科学崛起的好故事</a>。就“高影响力”（即高引用率）出版物而言，中国已超越美国和欧洲： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg" width="684" height="350.015625" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:393,&quot;width&quot;:768,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:684,&quot;bytes&quot;:78159,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ba02afc-e6da-4674-b353-382c462b09d6_768x393.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.economist.com/science-and-technology/2024/06/12/china-has-become-a-scientific-superpower">经济学人</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，我们必须对这些数字持保留态度。通过查看有多少其他论文引用它们来衡量论文的影响力可能是对真实影响力的有偏见的衡量——你可能有一群研究人员互相大量引用，从而夸大了指标。 Qiu、Steinwender 和 Azoulay<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32468">最近发表了一篇论文</a>，他们认为这种现象在中国尤其普遍：</p><blockquote><p>我们强调了与跨国比较特别相关的引文偏见的一个新来源：本土偏见，即研究人员过度引用本国研究人员的倾向……</p><p>我们发现，迄今为止，中国在所有国家中表现出最大的本土偏见。这并不是最近才出现的现象。尽管中国的本土偏见在过去二十年中一直在稳步增长，但在我们观察期开始的 2000 年，中国的引用已经出现了强烈的本土偏见。此外，中国的本土偏见并不是由任何特定的研究领域驱动的。相反，中国在 20 个广泛的科学领域中的 18 个领域表现出最强烈的本土偏见……</p><p>最后，我们发现本土偏见夸大了中国在科学领域的崛起。虽然中国在原始引用方面排名第二，仅次于美国，但一旦我们使用去偏见指标，它就会回落到第四位，落后于美国、英国和德国。如果人们认为家庭引用特别容易反映政治或战略考虑，而不是科学家基于他们选择引用的文章中包含的想法而积累的认可，那么家庭去偏见引用计数可能会被视为特别有用。</p></blockquote><p>研究人员基本上只是通过控制国家规模来识别“本土偏见”。他们对本土偏见的衡量仍然表现出某种明显的规模依赖性，欧洲小国处于规模的底部，而大国则位于顶部。所以我确实想知道他们是否正确控制了尺寸。但中国仍然绝对领先于包括印度在内的所有其他国家： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg" width="837" height="608" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:608,&quot;width&quot;:837,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:122202,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F383a6dc2-5d09-43aa-af8f-640b92e3b5f5_837x608.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32468">邱等人。 (2024)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>因此，虽然我认为作者关于英国在高影响力科学领域仍领先于中国的结论似乎很可疑，但就中国研究人员相互引用的次数而言，似乎确实发生了一些事情。</p><p>您可以用几种不同的方式来解释这一点。 <a href="https://blogs.lse.ac.uk/impactofsocialsciences/2023/03/29/standing-on-the-shoulders-of-chinese-scientific-giants-evidence-for-a-citation-discount-for-chinese-researchers/">一种可能</a>是，中国科学的质量比外国人想象的要高得多，而非汉语国家由于语言障碍而无法引用这些高质量的中国论文。另一种解释——Qiu 等人。建议——中国政府要求该国的研究人员出去撰写获得大量引用的论文，而研究人员基本上通过建立隐性或显性的<a href="https://scienceintegritydigest.com/2022/03/23/citation-statistics-and-citation-rings/">引用环</a>来回应。当然，这可能是这两种解释的某种组合。</p><p> （更新：在评论中，曾对作者署名膨胀进行<a href="https://psycnet.apa.org/buy/2024-30105-001">研究</a>并与中国科学家合作过的林志成<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/is-the-west-falling-behind-in-science/comment/59185842">提出了另一种解释</a>。他认为，中国研究人员比其他地方的研究人员承受着更大的压力，需要引用自己部门内的高级研究人员.)</p><p>此外，尚不清楚中国在科学方面的支出是否超过发达国家。正如《经济学人》文章所示，自 20 世纪 90 年代以来，中国的研发支出快速增长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0c92441d-0d9c-4dcf-bb3c-ca39a2afa0a1_384x444.jpeg 