hinapower.csis.org/china-research-and-development-rnd/">战略与国际研究中心</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><a href="https://chinapower.csis.org/china-research-and-development-rnd/">这些研究大部分是在国有企业的企业实验室中完成的</a>，这些企业早在 1999 年就接管了中国政府实验室的大部分研究职能。但中国大学的研发产出份额相当小，而且实际上已经最近<em>缩小了</em>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg" width="1200" height="1000" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1a813524-e603-479b-a319-2a5f51150cc5_1200x1000.jpeg&quot;,&quot;s