.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg" width="610" height="237.5929978118162" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:356,&quot;width&quot;:914,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:610,&quot;bytes&quot;:78957,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa6b847f8-2ba0-4ab5-a492-b46989baa63c_914x356.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></figure></div><p>等等。</p><p>这不是佩里的错。他在 2018 年发布原始图表时<a href="https://www.aei.org/carpe-diem/chart-of-the-day-century-price-changes-1997-to-2017/">表示</a>这只是一种<em>可能的</em>解释：</p><blockquote><p>看到任何图案吗？可贸易品（如电视等进口竞争）与不可贸易品（如儿童保育）、制成品（如服装和汽车等进口竞争）与服务（医疗、医院、教育）、竞争性行业（软件）与受保护行业（医疗保健） ）、政府参与/资助/监管的程度？</p></blockquote><p>但“政府参与程度”的解释似乎比“可贸易与不可贸易”和“制造业与服务业”的解释更受欢迎，尽管后者对于其中许多趋势来说是完全合理的解释。</p><p>事实上，当我们仔细观察这张图表时，我们可以发现与“政府参与程度”的叙述有很多差异。</p><p>大学教科书并未受到严格监管，但其价格却大幅上涨——至少到 2010 年代中期为止是这样。教科书是由廉价学生贷款间接补贴的，但在2009年至2012年政府从私营部门<a href="https://www.mercatus.org/research/data-visualizations/student-loans-held-federal-government">接管</a>学生贷款市场后不久，教科书的价格实际上就<em>停止了</em>上涨。</p><p>手机服务受到严格监管，但其价格却在图表中下降。与此同时，房地产可能是现有监管最严格的行业，并且也由政府通过税收减免和优惠券进行补贴，但在特定时期内其价格涨幅低于工资涨幅。</p><p>至于大学学费，私立学校的学费比公立学校高得多，自上世纪九十年代以来，其标价以美元计算的<a href="https://research.collegeboard.org/media/pdf/trends-in-college-pricing-presentation-2023.pdf">涨幅也更大</a>。</p><p>事实上，由于监管和补贴的共同作用而导致服务价格昂贵的流行观念并不能真正作为一个总括的解释。正如我去年在一篇文章中所写，在某些情况下，补贴是问题的一部分，在某些情况下，监管也是问题的一部分，但这里存在大量的细微差别和异质性： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;5a2ca274-a111-4924-9e5e-17c5a878b591&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;In a recent post over at his new substack (which you should check out), Marc Andreessen rails against the exploding prices of big-ticket service industries like college, health care, and child care. He posts the following famous graph from the American Enterprise Institute:&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Why do education, health care, and child care cost so much in America?&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-03-06T09:57:36.719Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c6c322c-d9a8-4d47-8374-3eb7cf7beb7d_1024x683.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-do-education-health-care-and&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:106662161,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:135,&quot;comment_count&quot;:134,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p> “政府参与”的故事也无法解释为什么许多从 20 世纪 90 年代末到 2010 年代初变得<em>更加难以</em>负担的服务在过去十年中变得<em>更加</em>负担得起： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg" width="656" height="476.6933333333333" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/bd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:654,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:656,&quot;bytes&quot;:78904,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbd6b2bae-5452-4375-9584-eb130c234223_900x654.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/jmhorp/status/1750622296283189542">杰里米·霍佩达尔</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>因此，虽然政府的参与几乎肯定在“世纪图表”中的一些价格差异中发挥了作用，但这可能只是众多因素之一。正如许多人所做的那样，将图表作为简单的“自由主义者是正确的”叙述的证据是错误的。</p><p>如果这里有一个重要的教训，那就是当图表显示许多不同的趋势时，您应该预期这些趋势有几个不同的原因。很少有“一种经济理论可以统治所有理论”，如果您认为图表已经证明了这种理论的存在，那么您很可能误解了图表。</p><h4>示例 2：生产力与薪酬</h4><p>过去十年来，在美国话语中，也许没有哪一张图表能像“生产率与薪酬”图表一样具有影响力。该图有很多版本，但我将使用经济政策研究所发布的版本。这可能是该图表最著名的版本——我们大多数人在 2010 年代末辩论这个问题时使用的版本： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F