"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg" width="800" height="600" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:600,&quot;width&quot;:800,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:31745,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff8dbf430-f12d-48f9-8226-4b7c267401af_800x600.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/ernietedeschi/status/1799098266166104142/photo/1">厄尼·特德斯基</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>因此，自大流行以来<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/LNU01373413">本土出生的劳动力参与率</a>小幅下降完全是由于54岁以上的人——换句话说，是人们提前退休造成的。本土出生的劳动力总数长期停滞是由于婴儿潮一代退休并且没有留下很多孩子。</p><p>换句话说，关于移民正在将本土出生的美国人赶出劳动力市场的“让美国再次伟大”论点完全是胡说八道。他们一定认为我们不知道如何阅读图表。</p><h4> 3. 对中国征收关税可以帮助其他发展中国家实现工业化</h4><p><a href="https://x.com/Noahpinion/status/1800592692378046517">英国专家</a>——甚至一些<a href="https://x.com/Noahpinion/status/1800617038312034514">美国专家</a>——继续猛烈抨击拜登对中国产品征收关税，而<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/in-which-british-writers-scold-america">完全无视关税背后的核心理由</a>。在他们的悲歌中搜索“军事”、“国防”和“国家安全”等词，结果却是一片空白。因为他们甚至没有解决关税最重要的原因，所以他们反对关税的论点不能被认真对待。</p><p>但除此之外，关税批评者还忽略了另一个重要的内容。关税为生产迁出中国提供了巨大的动力。但这并不意味着它会转移到美国——相反，它会转移到印度、墨西哥、越南、印度尼西亚、菲律宾等发展中国家。发展经济学家阿尔文德·萨勃拉曼尼安 (Arvind Subramanian) <a href="https://www.afr.com/policy/economy/how-higher-us-tariffs-are-helping-china-s-competitors-20240528-p5jh7s">写道</a>：</p><blockquote><p>关于<a href="https://www.afr.com/world/asia/us-china-protectionism-race-benefits-no-one-20240526-p5jgqe">中美竞争不断升级的</a>争论往往忽略了其他国家，尤其是较大的发展中经济体的观点。毕竟，这些关税不仅是保护主义的，而且是歧视性的……今天的关税是对来自中国等被视为对手的进口产品征收的，将经济活动转向<em>被</em>视为盟友的第三国供应商……</p><p>印度就是一个很好的例子。自2014年推出“中国加一”战略以来，它成功吸引了多家西方企业退出中国。值得注意的是，苹果已大幅扩大其在印度的iPhone制造业务， <a href="https://www.afr.com/technology/tesla-plant-likely-if-india-lowers-ev-tariffs-musk-20210725-p58cqg">据报道特斯拉也可能效仿</a>……如果印度能够建立一条供应链，在很大程度上独立于中国——电子行业正在缓慢发展的趋势——它可能会获得相对于中国及其相关国家的竞争优势……</p><p>美国的战略利益与第三国的能力和比较优势之间的重叠度越大，歧视性保护主义就越有可能长期存在，并为寻求多元化、远离残酷高效的中国的投资者提供确定性。</p></blockquote><p>当然，萨勃拉曼尼亚是对的，但我认为即使是他也走得不够远！萨勃拉曼尼亚只关注将生产转移到中国境外的<em>西方</em>公司，因此他认为，越南和印度尼西亚等供应链与中国一体化程度更高的国家受益较少。但这忽略了这些国家将从<em>中国</em>企业将生产迁出中国中受益的可能性。</p><p>目前，拜登的新关税仅针对中国。这意味着，如果像比亚迪这样的中国公司在越南建厂，他们就可以规避目前规定的关税。最终美国可能会堵住这个看似的漏洞（尽管欧洲可能不会）。但与此同时，中国企业去其他国家建厂的<a href="https://www.asiafinancial.com/chinese-firms-seen-shifting-production-abroad-to-avoid-us-tariffs">动力很大</a>。事实上，这正是他们正在做的事情： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg" width="670" height="477.93333333333334" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:642,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:670,&quot;bytes&quot;:47901,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff5ce6884-dc5d-480d-99fe-a20642903a46_900x642.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.ft.com/content/c77fefa3-7f47-429b-8149-50aa60f39498">英国《金融时报》</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>事实上，中国企业<a href="https://www.orfonline.org/research/to-stay-or-to-go-decoding-chinese-enterprises-india-dilemma">也在印度投资，尽管担心</a>从长远来看这将有助于印度成为中国的经济竞争对手。最终，个人激励通常胜过民族主义担忧。</p><p>即使你忽略这个问题的国家安全方面，你也应该同意公司将生产从中国转移到印度、越南、印度尼西亚等国家是一件非常好的事情。这些国家比中国贫穷得多，这意味着它们比中国更需要增长： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png" width="688" height="483.6235294117647" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:717,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:113313,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F97a4f203-5636-465c-9939-931e3864fd08_1020x717.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>归根结底，西方和中国企业将工厂迁往新一轮发展中国家，只是旧的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flying_geese_paradigm">“雁行论”发展论</a>的又一例证。但在这种情况下，鹅需要一点额外的推动才能离开中国。关税提供了这种推动力，全球穷人可能因此受益匪浅。</p><h4> 4. 租金管制有实际成本</h4><p>根据我的观察，租房者，以及像 YIMBY 这样致力于让租房者生活更轻松的人，都对租金管制的想法非常感兴趣。毕竟，给租房者带来直接痛苦的是……租金上涨。因此，想要<em>禁止痛苦的事情</em>，让眼前的痛苦消失，这是可以理解的。</p><p>人们普遍认为，租金管制可能会对租房者产生一些负面的<em>长期</em>后果——这项政策可能只是暂时的拐杖，让未来的情况变得更糟。但现在就是现在，明天就是明天，总是很容易<a href="https://x.com/alfred_twu/status/1800057440903581939">找到理由来说服自己</a>短期利益是不需要付出代价的。</p><p>但现实是，长期成本通常是存在的。康斯坦丁·霍洛迪林 (Konstantin Kholodilin) 对租金管制研究进行了<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1051137724000020?via%3Dihub">大量新文献综述</a>—— <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/180Pop64kR-RRSVx_jj_2wYc8J_C-WfWCL80NEePrLNY/edit?gid=0#gid=0">这是他引用的所有研究的电子表格</a>——他得出的结论是，其缺点是非常真实的：</p><blockquote><p>租金管制有用吗？还是它造成的损害比效用更大？……这项研究回顾了大量实证文献……租金管制在减缓受管制住宅的租金增长方面似乎相当有效。然而，这一政策也导致了影响全社会的多方面不良影响……</p><p> [A]根据这里审查的研究，通常，租金管制会导致<strong>不受管制的住宅租金更高</strong>。实行租金上限加剧了住房短缺问题。因此，等待的队列变得更长，潜在的租户必须花费更多的时间寻找住所......</p><p>同样，租金管制对<strong>新住宅建设和供应</strong>的影响似乎相似。大约三分之二的研究表明存在负面影响，而一些研究发现没有任何统计上显着的影响……[V]租金管制政策设计的变化可能很重要……[N]新建的住房可以不受管制，因此仍然存在不受租金管制法规的影响...</p><p>对于租金管制对住房质量的影响，已发表的研究几乎一致。除<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1051137724000020?via%3Dihub#bib0064">Gilderbloom (1986)</a>以及<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1051137724000020?via%3Dihub#bib0066">Gilderbloom 和 Markham (1996)</a>之外的所有研究都表明，租金管制会导致受监管的住宅<strong>质量下降</strong>。</p></blockquote><p>因此，虽然租金管制为那些有幸居住在租金管制单位的人们提供了很多好处，但它导致整体住房存量变得更小、更破旧。这不仅提高了租金，而且让他们更难找到搬家的地方，从而伤害了那些不住在租金管制单位的人。</p><p>这并不意味着租金管制永远不值得付出代价。但这意味着有代价，主张租金管制的人需要考虑一下。</p><h4> 5. 如今服务成本增长缓慢</h4><p>还记得那张图表显示医疗保健和教育等服务在美国变得越来越难以负担吗？ </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg" width="900" height="785" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:785,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:176711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa9f471fa-37c8-494f-b123-f4a2c02c3c65_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/Mark_J_Perry/status/1747995005518516419">马克·佩里</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这通常是一个非常好的和重要的图表。这不是一个<em>完美的</em>图表——它夸大了大学费用，因为它忽略了经济援助，而且它的数据来源可能低估了 <a href="https://research.collegeboard.org/media/pdf/trends-college-pricing-presentation-2022.pdf">最近学费的下降</a>。此外，它还使住房出现亏损，因为住房价格在绝对意义上上涨，尽管工资上涨更多。但这些都是小问题——总体而言，该图表准确地传达了这样一个事实：自世纪之交以来，尽管许多实物商品变得更加便宜，但大件服务的价格却变得越来越便宜。</p><p>但是，当您制作这样的“百分比增长”图表时，您选择的起始年份非常重要。如果改变起始年份，趋势通常看起来会非常不同。正如杰里米·霍佩达尔 (Jeremy Horpedahl)<a href="https://x.com/jmhorp/status/1750622296283189542">指出的</a>那样，许多自 2000 年以来变得更加难以负担的高价服务实际上自 2013 年以来变得更加<em>负担得起</em>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F799ba5c6-f311-4746-87f8-95f86376db2b_900x654.jpeg" width="696" height="505.76" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;