onent-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png" width="788" height="474" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:474,&quot;width&quot;:788,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:20022,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>电动自行车<a href="https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2022/01/19/2369598/0/en/Global-Electric-Bike-Market-Share-Poised-to-Reflect-14-9-CAGR-by-2028-to-Hit-USD-69-24-Billion-Eco-Friendly-Mobility-is-Boosting-e-Bikes-Demand-Says-Facts-Factors.html">在全球的价值已达 400 亿美元</a>，并且增长迅速。</p><p>电动自行车与普通自行车不同——它们为您的肌肉力量增加电力，使骑行更加轻松。这从两个方面改变了自行车运动。首先，它可以让你走得更远。挪威<a href="https://www.treehugger.com/e-bikers-ride-much-farther-and-more-frequently-than-regula-bikers-5076231">最近的一项研究表明</a>：</p><blockquote><blockquote><p>购买电动自行车的人平均每天使用自行车的里程从 2.1 公里（1.3 英里）增加到 9.2 公里（5.7 英里）；增长 340%。电动自行车在所有交通中的份额也急剧增加。从 17% 到 49%，他们骑电动自行车而不是步行、乘坐公共交通和开车……[I]事实上，人们骑电动自行车的时间越长[.]</p></blockquote></blockquote><p>其次，电动自行车使<a href="https://cyclebaron.com/how-good-are-electric-bikes-going-uphill/">骑自行车上坡变得非常容易</a>。这为骑自行车的人开放了以前基本上被拒绝的广阔区域（例如旧金山的大部分地区）。</p><p>更长的续航里程和不必担心道路坡度的结合意味着电动自行车有可能改变我们的生活方式。由于美国已经有了道路，并且可以在尚不存在的地方添加自行车道，因此改造城市以容纳大量电动自行车通勤者的成本不会很大（当然比建造火车要小！）。由于电动自行车体积小且易于停车，我们可以在常见目的地附近建造许多自行车停放架，从而省去通勤时寻找停车位的一些麻烦。</p><p>总而言之，电动自行车将使我们的城市出行变得更加容易，这有望增加人与人之间的联系，让我们感到更加自由。它们还将使许多领域的食品和产品交付变得更加容易。而且由于电动自行车仍然需要消耗一点肌肉力量，我们也可能会变得更健康一点！</p><p>还值得注意的是，电动<a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90738126/this-startup-designed-an-electric-cargo-ship-to-cross-the-ocean">货船</a>和<a href="https://www.afar.com/magazine/electric-planes-are-coming-sooner-than-you-think">飞机</a>正在酝酿之中，尽管我预计这些在未来十年不会变得普遍。</p><h4>无人机是战争的未来</h4><p>电池不仅会改变民用交通，还将改变军用车辆，从而带来全新的战争方式。任何关注乌克兰战争的人都知道这一点。尽管像 Bayraktar 这样的内燃机无人机最受关注，但小型电动无人机已经开始在战场上相对较近的距离进行精确打击。这是一个视频： </p><div data-component-name="Twitter2ToDOM" class="tweet" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/kirbygriffin17/status/1561980980440616960&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Ukrainian Drone Drops Grenade directly into a Russian Tank with crew sti... <a class=\&quot;tweet-url\&quot; href=\&quot;https://youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lpocd4?feature=share\&quot;>youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lp&#8230;</a> via <span class=\&quot;tweet-fake-link\&quot;>@YouTube</span>&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;kirbygriffin17&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;kirby griffin&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Tue Aug 23 07:37:40 +0000 2022&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:1,&quot;like_count&quot;:1,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lpocd4?feature=share&quot;,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3b0ec7cd-52a1-4119-942e-aa5129c10594_480x360.jpeg&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Ukrainian Drone