/span>转发</span></div></div></div><p>这不仅仅是因为乌克兰钱少，被迫诉诸廉价的蹩脚武器；<a href="https://twitter.com/RALee85/status/1560404144132964355">俄罗斯人也在使用电池供电的无人机</a>。当然，这些无人机对于战场侦察也<a href="https://www.stimson.org/2022/drone-warfare-in-ukraine-understanding-the-landscape/">非常有用</a>，这对于瞄准现代精确武器至关重要。</p><p>廉价可靠的能量密集型电池的出现使这成为可能。电池供电的无人机体积小、价格便宜且相对安静。在地缘政治竞争和冲突加剧的时代，军用无人机的创新可能才刚刚开始。杀伤人员无人机可能正在路上，它可以将士兵从密集的城市地区清除，同时对周围结构造成的损害最小。 <a href="https://www.extremetech.com/extreme/335095-scientists-develop-swarm-of-inescapable-autonomous-drones">自主集群无人机</a>也在开发中。电池供电的机器人可以<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2021/4/7/22371590/boston-dynamics-spot-robot-military-exercises-french-army">帮助携带设备穿越战场</a>，甚至携带和发射以前为步兵保留的武器。</p><p>在极端情况下，人类可能会被彻底赶出战场。电池体积小、重量轻、价格便宜，可能对此至关重要。</p><h4>一切都由电池供电</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f